/***********************************
 * Calculates the inverse hyperbolic sine of x.
 *
 *  Mathematically,
 *  ---------------
 *  asinh(x) =  log( x + sqrt( x*x + 1 )) // if x >= +0
 *  asinh(x) = -log(-x + sqrt( x*x + 1 )) // if x <= -0
 *  -------------
